Cost-effectiveness of combined oral bisphosphonate therapy and falls prevention 
exercise for fracture prevention in the USA.

Mori T(1)(2)(3), Crandall CJ(4), Ganz DA(5)(6)(7).

Author information:
(1)Department of General Internal Medicine, Kameda Medical Center, 929 
Higashi-cho, Kamogawa City, Chiba, 296-8602, Japan. takahiromori@outlook.com.
(2)Department of Primary Care and Medical Education, Graduate School of 
