777. Nurs Older People. 2006 Apr 1;18(3):38. doi: 10.7748/nop.18.3.38.s18.

The truth about ageing in the future.

Allen D.

Every minute that you spend reading this article, the average life expectancy in 
Britain will rise by 12 seconds. That was the arresting claim made at the start 
of a four- page feature by Alok Jha in The Guardian on 'the future of old age'. 
So by this time tomorrow, life expectancy will have risen by nearly five hours. 
